{"tid":2087948,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民間記者會籲上街︰反抗聲要響亮","createTime":"2020-07-01T02:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T02:48:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f3eecbf057bf243ef9c539860249d0e3cc37c594","tid":2087948,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:16:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200701/AEXO7HSYF2QLCU4TUCPS4OOL3U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2FAEXO7HSYF2QLCU4TUCPS4OOL3U%2F&d=6wD9ZzBID4i2v0E%2BCeDzwAhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=0b9eae2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200701%2FAEXO7HSYF2QLCU4TUCPS4OOL3U%2F&h=77f33910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200701/AEXO7HSYF2QLCU4TUCPS4OOL3U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會籲上街︰反抗聲要響亮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EpkgtF7Y5U2l5OSL6ThuEgif6yo=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWMSINF3XPWV5RFQDYLOA7ZTVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEpkgtF7Y5U2l5OSL6ThuEgif6yo%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWMSINF3XPWV5RFQDYLOA7ZTVY.jpg&h=8755e8a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民間記者會昨號召港人今日上街，痛擊暴政。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】民間記者會形容，港版國安法等同宣告「香港已死」，但強調港人已退無可退，號召港人今日上街，痛擊暴政，讓國際社會聽見港人響亮的反抗聲音。<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會發言人表示，過往7.1對港人的意義除了假期外，還有回歸。但在今年，7.1的意義變為「不畏強權、不懼國安法」，港人仍能走上街頭，向國際社會宣示要爭取自由、民主制度的決心。他續說，7.1對中共意義重大，但對抗爭者而言，卻是香港滅亡的開始，港人必須浴火重生，今日上街繼續對外宣示意志，「我哋嘅反抗之聲要足夠響亮，大聲話畀國際社會、大聲話畀犧牲嘅手足知，我哋仍然有人留低、會沉着應戰，以人數回應以恐懼治國嘅中共：呢一招（港版國安法）唔work！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n周竪峰堅持「香港獨立」 口號<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：人治立法 充斥「例外」程序<br />\n<br />\n發言人預料，國安法實施<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n香港人嘅信念」。<br />\n<br />\n多次高調表態支<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n今日會現身街頭。<br />\n<br />\n面對昨日多個政治人物宣告退出社運，民間記者會發言人認為抗爭的熱度及難度與政治人物退出沒有太大關係，即使有不少人說示威活動未有太多人參加，但相信「創意爆棚」的港人將會有不同方法繼續抗爭，甚至把抗爭地下化。"},{"pid":"51f0a7d6b884daacd3c6a2d8223688bce97a50a2","tid":2087948,"uid":140538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:22:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafVnYEV.jpg&amp;h=79d38c5d&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"c5cdda7976e49987e8e4710c581e81db1e23ee15","tid":2087948,"uid":242262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCh6gYZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCh6gYZ.jpg&h=d092b463&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d37ad8eb51f9ba8941b64393f26f063827a9fe14","tid":2087948,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T02:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}